title: ET Defence Bulletin: In a show of strength, Indian Navy fires Brahmos missile from INS Chennai
text:
NEW DELHI: Below is a list of the top defence stories of today. 

Hover over the image below and click on the icons to read the stories. 

The ongoing war drill TROPEX 2017 where in a show of strength, Indian Navy fired Surface to Surface Brahmos missile from INS Chennai, the confrontation between Iran and America, the surprise case of 59 trainee CoBRA commandos 'bunking' duties that prompted CRPF to order an inquiry, India's urgent arms deals of Rs 20,000 crore, China 's military exercised aimed at India, Japan and US, and developing of a combat ready aircraft jointly by India and UK are some of the key defence related developments of the day.
